# GM-1: Skill Gap Detection
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any task that cannot be handled by an existing skill

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Skill Gap: A task or request that cannot be executed by any existing skill.

ENFORCE: Tasks with no applicable skill must not proceed; a new skill definition must be requested.
PROHIBIT: Attempting execution of unhandled tasks.
ON VIOLATION: Halt task execution → request prompt engineer intervention.
